snippet.title: Speedway Blast for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Speedway Blast is an action game, where you have to collect fuel diamonds and shoot asphalt monsters and their eggs.

An asphalt monster might come out of an egg, so you better be careful!

Shooting eggs or asphalt monsters will refill your fuel.

If you drive into a house, bridge, or tree your car will be destroyed!


What I think:

Quite fun game.....too bad you can't reverse.
